Mizoguchi" title="Kenji Mizoguchi">Kenji Mizoguchi</a></li>\n<li><i><a href="/wiki/A_Geisha" title="A Geisha">A Geisha</a></i> (<span class="t_nihongo_kanji"><span lang="ja" xml:lang="ja">\xe7\xa5\x87\xe5\x9c\x92\xe5\x9b\x83\xe5\xad\x90</span></span>, <i>Gion bayashi</i>) (1953)\xe2\x80\x94Dir. <a href="/wiki/Kenji_Mizoguchi" title="Kenji Mizoguchi">Kenji Mizoguchi</a></li>\n<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Teahouse_of_the_August_Moon_(film)" title="The Teahouse of the August Moon (film)">The Teahouse of the August Moon</a></i> (1956)\xe2\x80\x94Dir. <a href="/wiki/Daniel_Mann" title="Daniel Mann">Daniel Mann</a></li>\n<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Barbarian_and_the_Geisha" title="The Barbarian and the Geisha">The Barbarian and the Geisha</a></i> (1958)\xe2\x80\x94Dir. <a href="/wiki/John_Huston" title="John Huston">John Huston</a></li>\n<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Geisha_Boy" title="The Geisha Boy">The Geisha Boy</a></i> (1958)\xe2\x80\x94Dir. <a href="/wiki/Frank_Tashlin" title="Frank Tashlin">Frank Tashlin</a></li>\n<li><i><a href="/wiki/Late_Chrysanthemums" title="Late Chrysanthemums">Late Chrysanthemums</a></i> (Bangiku) (1958)\xe2\x80\x94Dir. <a href="/wiki/Mikio_Naruse" title="Mikio Naruse">Mikio Naruse</a></li>\n<li><i><a href="/wiki/Cry_for_Happy" title="Cry for Happy">Cry for Happy</a></i> (1961)\xe2\x80\x94George Marshall comedy</li>\n<li><i><a href="/wiki/My_Geisha" title="My Geisha">My Geisha</a></i> (1962)\xe2\x80\x94Dir. <a href="/wiki/Jack_Cardiff" title="Jack Cardiff">Jack Cardiff</a></li>\n<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Wolves_(film)" class="mw-redirect" title="The Wolves (film)">The Wolves</a></i> (1971)\xe2\x80\x94Dir. <a href="/wiki/Hideo_Gosha" title="Hideo Gosha">Hideo Gosha</a></li>\n<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_World_of_Geisha" title="The World of Geisha">The World of Geisha</a></i> (1973)\xe2\x80\x94Dir. <a href="/wiki/Tatsumi_Kumashiro" title="Tatsumi Kumashiro">Tatsumi Kumashiro</a></li>\n<li><i><a href="/wiki/In_the_Realm_of_the_Senses" title="In the Realm of the Senses">In the Realm of the Senses</a></i> (1976)\xe2\x80\x94Dir. <a href="/wiki/Nagisa_Oshima" title="Nagisa Oshima">Nagisa Oshima</a></li>\n<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Ihara_Saikaku_Koshoku_Ichidai_Otoko&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Ihara Saikaku Koshoku Ichidai Otoko (page does not exist)">Ihara Saikaku Koshoku Ichidai Otoko</a></i> (1991)\xe2\x80\x94Dir. <a href="/w/index.php?title=Yukio_Abe&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Yukio Abe (page does not exist)">Yukio Abe</a></li>\n<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Geisha_House" title="The Geisha House">The Geisha House</a></i> (1999)\xe2\x80\x94Dir. <a href="/wiki/Kinji_Fukasaku" title="Kinji Fukasaku">Kinji Fukasaku</a></li>\n<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=The_Sea_is_Watching&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="The Sea is Watching (page does not exist)">The Sea is Watching</a></i> (2002)\xe2\x80\x94Dir. <a href="/wiki/Kei_Kumai" title="Kei Kumai">Kei Kumai</a></li>\n<li><i><a href="/wiki/Zatoichi" title="Zatoichi">Zatoichi</a></i> (2003)\xe2\x80\x94Dir. <a href="/wiki/Takeshi_Kitano" title="Takeshi Kitano">Takeshi Kitano</a></li>\n<li><i><a href="/wiki/Fighter_in_the_Wind" title="Fighter in the Wind">Fighter in the Wind</a></i> (2004)\xe2\x80\x94Dir. <a href="/wiki/Yang_Yun-ho" title="Yang Yun-ho">Yang Yun-ho</a></li>\n<li><i><a href="/wiki/Memoirs_of_a_Geisha_(film)" title="Memoirs of a Geisha (film)">Memoirs of a Geisha</a></i> (2005)\xe2\x80\x94Dir. <a href="/wiki/Rob_Marshall" title="Rob Marshall">Rob Marshall</a></li>\n<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wakeful_Nights&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Wakeful Nights (page does not exist)">Wakeful Nights</a></i> (2005)\xe2\x80\x94Dir. <a href="/wiki/Masahiko_Tsugawa" title="Masahiko Tsugawa">Masahiko Tsugawa</a></li>\n<li><i><a href="/wiki/Maiko_Haaaan!!!" title="Maiko Haaaan!!!">Maiko Haaaan!!!</a></i> (2007)\xe2\x80\x94Dir. <a href="/w/index.php?title=Nobuo_Mizuta&amp;action=edit&amp;